          </entryLinks>
          <rules>
            <rule name="Attached Deployment" id="c60c-f117-8190-511d" hidden="false">
              <description>Each Independent Techmarine must be assigned to a unit of non-jump pack infantry before the battle beings. He may not purchase a Jump Pack. If there is a Space Marine Bike Squadron or Attack Bike Squadron included in the army he may purchase a Space Marine Bike, but must be attached to one of those instead.</description>
            </rule>
            <rule name="Armoured Support" id="ebbd-e56e-1781-2754" hidden="false">
              <description>The Independent Techmarine may attempt to repair a Space Marine Vehicle with his servo-arm, even if he is being transported within it. It will repair an immobilized vehicle on a 5 or 6.</description>
            </rule>
          </rules>
        </selectionEntry>
      </selectionEntries>
