      <rules>
        <rule name="War Relic" id="234c-bc57-3ead-8f47" hidden="false">
          <description>A Model upgraded to a War Relic ignores the first Glancing OR Penetrating hit it receives in a battle. If a War Relic is destroyed, every Novamarines unit within 6&quot; must take a pinning test.</description>
